{"tid":1682902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線新諗法 - United State/UK/Australia/Canada is NOT China","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T08:19:10.000Z","uid":71447,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cdeaab01e7ad480b02f2dc5dffaf09195b88255a","tid":1682902,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"由今年６月開始<br />\n國際戰線一直浮浮沉沉<br />\n近一兩個月終見少少曙光<br />\n但係始終未夠<br />\n個人認為係時侯再進一步<br />\n<br />\n之前大家嘗試推赤納粹 #Chinazi<br />\n結果算喺還可以<br />\n始終爭議性大<br />\n而且有D到喉唔到肉<br />\n海外迴響唔大<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最近我諗下有嘜新口號可以用<br />\n諗番起<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong is not China</span><br />\n其實可以演繹出去成為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">United State is not China</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">United Kingdom is not China</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">Australia is not China</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">Canada is not China</span><br />\n諸如此類<br />\n咁樣對應番去宣傳<br />\n應該比就咁話 #Chinazi 一句到尾更到肉</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNBA事件希望可以靠United State is not China繼續煲大佢<br />\n煲起美英澳加個愛國心時<br />\n絕對會對以後事半功倍<br />\n希望大家討論下呢個下一步行唔行得過<br />\n多謝睇晒呢段的你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人<br />\n反抗</strong></span>"},{"pid":"13acb86c9fc9afcd756118d1d27aaa85905316fa","tid":1682902,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"推一推 01/10"},{"pid":"707810a74de3014ce1c076314d3a41fcae9d60bf","tid":1682902,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"推一推 02/10"},{"pid":"762ef4c035aa7cfbee1ba21f428f69db287ca9c1","tid":1682902,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"推一推 03/10"},{"pid":"aa614e566d0a5b57d28b7ec1b81aad42b21ce742","tid":1682902,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"推一推 04/10"},{"pi